# Environment Variables for Local GPT

# Cloud AI Options (Choose one - for fallback when Ollama is not available)

# Option 1: OpenAI (GPT models)
# Get your API key from: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
# VITE_OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-your-openai-api-key-here

# Option 2: Groq (Ultra-fast Llama inference) - RECOMMENDED for Ollama-like experience
# Get your API key from: https://console.groq.com/keys
# VITE_GROQ_API_KEY=gsk_your-groq-api-key-here

# Option 3: Together AI (Open source models including Llama)
# Get your API key from: https://api.together.xyz/settings/api-keys
# VITE_TOGETHER_API_KEY=your-together-api-key-here

# Option 4: Replicate (Hosted open source models)
# Get your API key from: https://replicate.com/account/api-tokens
# VITE_REPLICATE_API_KEY=r8_your-replicate-api-key-here

# Notes:
# - Choose ONE of the above options
# - Groq is recommended for the closest Ollama-like experience (fast Llama models)
# - If none are set, the app works in demo mode when Ollama is unavailable
# - Local Ollama will always be preferred when available
